    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> (the same as you would for pasta)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>",
