    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then chop into bite-size pieces</p><p>Chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
