    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat and add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped courgette</strong> and cook for 6-8 min or until tender</p>",
