    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the courgette is cooked, fluff the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>bulgur </strong>with a fork and add to the pan</p><p>Break your <strong>goats' cheese</strong> into chunks</p><p>Stir <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>goats' cheese chunks </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>green</strong> <strong>chutney</strong> through the bulgur<strong> </strong>(save the rest for the garnish!) – this is your <strong>goats' cheese & bulgur salad</strong></p>",
