      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>goats' cheese & bulgur salad</strong> with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>goats' cheese chunks</strong> and <strong>green</strong> <strong>chutney</strong> over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
